As the end of 2022 approaches here is an end to it.. so much growth & healing. Learned so much about myself. I view life so different after my brothers passing.. Now i truly enjoy every moment with the people I love. I find inspiration in life. I take risks & don’t feed into anything that doesn’t feed my soul. I’ve set boundaries, spoke up for myself & prioritized myself. Life isn’t ever promised so let’s enjoy it & fuck the negatives. Give me my flowers now not when im gone. We cry but then we laugh. More trips, more love, more good health, more wealth 2023 🥂
